snippet.title: Terraria: Otherworld - GDC 2015 Trailer
snippet.description:
Collection of Terraria: Otherworld in-game footage first shown at the Re-Logic / Engine Software Booth at the Game Developers Conference (GDC) on March 3rd 2015. For more information check the following links:
http://forums.terraria.org/index.php?threads/terraria-otherworld-post-gdc-details-trailer.13943/
or simply http://www.terrariaotherworld.com
